he signed the order on saturday 
the new limit is 188000 for all services although the air 
force and coast guard totals were not changed on nov 14 cheney 
had raised the overall ceiling from 50000 to 125000 
a total of 96834 members of the army navy air force marine 
corps and coast guard reserves and national guard are on active 
duty under callup authority granted by president bush on aug 23 
thousands more have been alerted to prepare to mobilize 
the pentagon gave no reason for increasing the callup limit 
