pitch for the reservists in congressional testimony monday he said 
their participation in desert shield has been a significant 
factor in affording us flexibility and balance 
the current callup of reserves is the first since the vietnam 
war and the largest since the 1961 crisis triggered by east 
germanys construction of the berlin wall 
cheneys latest order means the pentagon may approach the legal 
limit for reserve activations short of declaring war or a national 
emergency the president is limited to authorizing the callup of 
200000 reservists 
the secretarys move also indicates that the services are 
relying much more on reserve manpower to fill out a second wave of 
troop deployments to the persian gulf than they did in an initial 
deployment of 240000 air ground and sea forces 
