the military rebellion that 
turned parts of buenos aires into a battleground two days before 
president bush is to arrive was argentinas fourth since 1987 and 
may have been the least effective 
challenged immediately by the air and armored power of loyalist 
troops mondays was the shortest and bloodiest of the four 
