troops getting a rare break from 
desert duty made christmas messages on videotape tuesday for loved 
ones back home one marine donned a santa cap another put on his 
gas mask 
and one homesick soldier mouthed a tender i love you for his 
wife before getting up from his chair to kiss the camera lens 
