relaxation center better known as desert world troops sit in 
front of one of eight video cameras to make 15minute messages 
called better than a letter 
chief warrant officer randall anderson 33 of swainsboro ga 
put on a pair of santa claus suspenders and a redandwhite 
stocking cap his wife sent him the only other things he wore were 
his marine corps gym shorts and shower shoes 
