creatures cavorting on the tv screen 
can cats really see a tv video 
veterinarians agree with malarkey that although cats dont 
discern shapes and colors as distinctly as humans they are acutely 
aware of moving figures and sounds that excite them 
malarkey says hes plowing the profits from video catnip 
into a series of sequels with bigger birds bigger squirrels 
maybe some sea gulls thrown in 
