quibble with a jurys verdict 
hawkins killing was the most serious racial incident in the 
city since the 1986 killing of a 23yearold black man in howard 
beach in that confrontation the victim was struck and killed by a 
car after a mob of whites chased him onto a highway 
hawkins 16 was slain when he and three friends all black 
teenagers went to bensonhurst to look at a used car the unarmed 
youths attracted the attention of a mob of as many as 30 
batwielding whites looking for a fight 
