about being off to write about the food in southeast asia 
the streets of old havana were replicated for the film shot 
almost entirely in the dominican republic but owen roizmans 
photography is merely pedestrian judith rascoe wholl stop the 
rain endless love wrote the screenplay 
produced by pollack and richard roth with ronald l schwary as 
executive producer universal pictures havana is rated r 
